{"tid":1733125,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"教育局宣布全港學校明日繼續停課","createTime":"2019-11-18T04:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T05:36:54.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5097dc6cf212ab7b191fa4e365fd4b7dbc4d3ad0","tid":1733125,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:47:24.000Z","msg":"教育局宣布，全港學校明日繼續停課。如情況許可，學校最快將於星期二復課。<br />\n<br />\n局方表示，雖然全港道路及公共運輸服務逐步恢復，但目前尚有不穩定因素；而星期一亦是周末後第一個繁忙的工作日，基於安全考慮，全港學校，包括幼稚園、小學、中學及特殊學校，明日繼續停課，並應為日後復課作好準備。停課期間，學校必須保持校舍開放，家長如有需要可將子女送返學校。<br />\n<br />\n局方呼籲，各界應立刻停止一切暴力破壞活動，讓學生可以恢復正常的學校生活。教育局再次提醒學生應留在家中，不要在街上流連，遠離危險，更切勿參加違法活動。"},{"pid":"602e2728b98896ee8abc71d03c57cbffb2486e18","tid":1733125,"uid":332860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:48:05.000Z","msg":"拉 old news"},{"pid":"2e6a9155e29f200435546dd79b768a57371c9e76","tid":1733125,"uid":332304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:48:35.000Z","msg":"Old news<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"8ffa5fcd723ab4e25c3b9cd1b1549e1f18dafc27","tid":1733125,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"0deff2ffccbcafc22749583cd2ae09a4d9cbad0c","tid":1733125,"uid":327787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:58:19.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"a19b5bf545394fdaec9d281626fac443efb1fe1c","tid":1733125,"uid":338154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"58c15a75df11ed724bbc5f06e2fc03b78a1ca3e5","tid":1733125,"uid":264022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"拉乜<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191118/mobile/bkn-20191118132644026-1118_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191118%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191118132644026-1118_00822_001.html&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2akErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&